    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "大家好，我是周航。苏晴今天嗓子听着有点哑啊，昨晚又熬夜刷论文了？",
      "start": 7.805,
      "duration": 6.487,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "别提了，昨晚看到一份关于AI治理的报告，越看越精神，根本睡不着。我跟你说，今天咱们要聊的话题特别有意思。",
      "start": 14.789,
      "duration": 13.322,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "是嘛，我看大纲了。说实话，第一条看完我还愣了一下——讲哲学？AI播客讲哲学？",
      "start": 28.564,
      "duration": 7.576,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对啊，你看这个标题，\"冷门的哲学，成了'治'AI的热门\"。你是不是也觉得很新鲜？",
      "start": 36.545,
      "duration": 6.922,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "说实话，我第一反应是……哲学家终于有饭吃了？但仔细想想这事儿其实挺严肃的。AI以前咱们聊的都是模型多强、参数多少，现在突然冒出来一个\"价值对齐\"、\"责任边界\"，这风向不对啊。",
      "start": 43.9,
      "duration": 17.304,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我也是这种感觉。你想啊，前几年大家都在卷算力、卷数据、卷模型架构，工程师说了算对吧？现在呢？规则制定这场子，慢慢地要由哲学背景的人来参与了。",
      "start": 61.669,
      "duration": 16.718,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，这不是说工程师不重要了，而是维度变了。技术能解决\"能不能做\"的问题，但\"该不该做\"这个问题，工程师答不上来。你让一个搞Transformer的人去讲电车难题，他能给你讲出花来吗？",
      "start": 78.849,
      "duration": 16.215,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈哈哈确实。我看到大纲里有一句话特别戳我——说未来各国和企业的AI竞争力，不仅取决于算力和算法，更取决于治理哲学的成熟度与话语权。这话分量很重啊。",
      "start": 95.515,
      "duration": 17.391,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "重在哪呢？重在\"话语权\"这三个字。你看现在欧盟搞AI法案，美国搞各种行政令，咱们国家也在推自己的标准框架。这些东西表面上是法律条文，骨子里全是哲学问题——什么叫公平？什么叫透明？什么叫可解释？",
      "start": 113.406,
      "duration": 16.999,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，而且我发现一个特别有意思的现象。最近好多科技公司招人，开始列一个奇怪的要求：哲学博士优先。你以前见过这种招聘吗？",
      "start": 130.843,
      "duration": 10.101,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我跟你说，这不是开玩笑。我上个月还看到一家做AGI的公司，专门设了个\"首席哲学家\"的岗位，年薪开得比很多技术VP都高。说白了，他们是真意识到，光靠技术跑得快没用，跑偏了更麻烦。",
      "start": 141.405,
      "duration": 15.649,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯，这就让我想到主编给的那句金句——AI的竞争已从模型本身延伸至治理哲学与算力底座，技术之外的软实力和硬基础设施同样决定未来格局。",
      "start": 157.499,
      "duration": 16.738,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个总结挺到位的。算力是硬的，算法是软的，但治理哲学是介于两者之间的东西——它没芯片那么硬，但影响比算法还要深远。",
      "start": 174.711,
      "duration": 11.276,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那咱们接着聊第二个头条，这个我觉得对咱们国家AI产业特别关键。\"不靠英伟达网卡，国产GPU直通方案实测出炉：吞吐飙升、延迟砍半\"。",
      "start": 186.414,
      "duration": 14.3,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这事儿我必须好好说说。你知道这意味着什么吗？以前国产GPU一直被诟病什么？单卡性能其实还行，但一上集群就拉胯，问题就出在互联上。",
      "start": 201.178,
      "duration": 12.713,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "等等，你给没听过技术细节的听众解释一下，啥叫RDMA？为啥这么重要？",
      "start": 214.308,
      "duration": 8.403,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "行，我打个比方。你把GPU想象成工厂里的工人，单个工人干活挺快，但要几百个工人协同完成一个大项目，中间通信就特别关键。RDMA就是那种\"工人之间能直接对话、绕过所有中间人\"的通信方式，延迟极低，吞吐极高。",
      "start": 223.147,
      "duration": 20.612,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哦明白了。那英伟达的网卡在里头扮演啥角色？",
      "start": 244.176,
      "duration": 4.92,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "以前大家都用英伟达的ConnectX系列网卡，就因为它支持RDMA而且性能顶呱呱。但你想啊，国产GPU用别人家的网卡做互联，等于脖子还是被别人卡着。这次不一样了，国产GPU终于在RDMA层面摆脱了对英伟达的依赖。",
      "start": 249.592,
      "duration": 25.14,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "而且大纲里说\"吞吐飙升、延迟砍半\"，这个数据很硬核啊。",
      "start": 275.144,
      "duration": 7.271,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这可不是PPT数据，是实测出来的。这事儿如果放在三年前说出来，估计没人信。但现在做到了，这就是\"系统级替代\"——不是单点替代，是从芯片到互联到软件栈，整套东西咱们自己能玩了。",
      "start": 282.894,
      "duration": 17.26,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我跟你说，这事儿对咱们普通人也有影响。你想啊，国产算力一旦真正自主了，大模型训练成本能降下来，以后咱们用AI产品的费用可能也会更便宜。而且最关键的，供应链安全这事儿，再也不用担心被\"卡脖子\"了。",
      "start": 300.586,
      "duration": 20.656,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，这是里程碑意义。之前是\"能不能造出来\"的问题，现在是\"造出来能不能用好\"的问题。这两个问题的难度完全不在一个量级。",
      "start": 321.71,
      "duration": 11.034,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_024_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_024_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯，所以我觉得这条新闻和头条一其实是呼应起来的。头条一说软实力——治理哲学，这条说硬底座——算力基础设施。一个管方向，一个管执行，AI这块拼图越来越完整了。",
      "start": 333.234,
      "duration": 15.978,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_025_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_025_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个观察挺到位的。咱们接着聊快讯，第一条，商汤大装置和国信数算达成战略合作，要共建算力网试验场。",
      "start": 349.689,
      "duration": 9.056,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_026_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_026_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这事儿我理解就是响应\"全国一体化算力网\"的号召吧？现在各地都在搞算力中心，但都是散的，怎么把它们串起来是个大问题。",
      "start": 359.163,
      "duration": 10.971,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_027_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_027_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，\"一体化\"这三个字背后是国家层面的算力调度思路。东部算力贵、西部算力便宜，怎么把西部便宜算力调度到东部用？这就像电力网络一样，算力也要搞\"西电东送\"。",
      "start": 370.573,
      "duration": 15.867,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_028_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_028_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈，这个类比妙。所以商汤和国信数算的合作，本质上是把\"算力调度\"这个事儿落地做试验田对吧？",
      "start": 386.852,
      "duration": 9.23,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_029_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_029_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，而且商汤自己有模型、有人才，国信数算有数据中心、有客户资源，两家合作能把\"算力—模型—应用\"这条链路打通。这种合作如果跑通了，后面会有更多玩家跟进。",
      "start": 396.575,
      "duration": 12.495,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_030_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_030_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "行，那咱们看看快讯二。WAIC端侧原生架构获产业共识，Om AI联汇正式发起物理AI协同发展倡议。",
      "start": 409.479,
      "duration": 14.106,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_031_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_031_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "端侧AI这个赛道，今年是真的起来了。说白了，就是AI不再非得跑在云端数据中心里，可以直接在你手机、你车、你家里那些设备上跑。",
      "start": 424.072,
      "duration": 11.929,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_032_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_032_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，你看现在手机厂商、汽车厂商都在卷这个。这次Om AI联汇发起的\"物理AI协同发展倡议\"，听着挺新鲜的——物理AI是个啥概念？",
      "start": 436.443,
      "duration": 11.363,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_033_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_033_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我跟你讲，物理AI就是让AI不只是处理文字图片，而是能跟真实物理世界打交道。比如机器人、自动驾驶、智能工厂里的机械臂，这些都需要AI理解和操控物理环境。这跟你手机上聊天画图完全不是一个level。",
      "start": 448.266,
      "duration": 19.48,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_034_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_034_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哦，那Om AI联汇是个什么组织？",
      "start": 468.217,
      "duration": 3.701,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_035_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_035_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我查了下，它是这次WAIC期间成立的一个产业联盟性质的东西，把做端侧芯片、做模型、做应用的公司拢到一块儿。大家约定好接口协议、数据格式，避免重复造轮子，一起把生态做大。",
      "start": 472.33,
      "duration": 16.259,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_036_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_036_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这个思路挺对的。说白了就是——以前大家各干各的，互不兼容，最后市场做不大。现在先定标准、再搞技术，反而是更高效的做法。",
      "start": 489.034,
      "duration": 10.797,
